748
00:41:19,076 --> 00:41:20,344
I was just joking.

749
00:41:20,411 --> 00:41:21,479
Of course, you were!

750
00:41:21,545 --> 00:41:23,280
Don't go, Akitsu! Don't read the room!

751
00:41:23,347 --> 00:41:24,915
You'll make things awkward.

752
00:41:24,982 --> 00:41:26,317
He left so quickly.

753
00:41:35,526 --> 00:41:39,763
Earlier, why did I call you again?

754
00:41:40,831 --> 00:41:45,202
Why? You wanted me
to get baby wipes, didn't you?

755
00:41:48,739 --> 00:41:50,241
You said,

756
00:41:51,408 --> 00:41:55,746
"What you want me to do
is what I can do for you."

757
00:41:59,250 --> 00:42:00,751
It made me happy.

758
00:42:02,586 --> 00:42:05,222
Even though my husband
and the ward office abandoned me,

759
00:42:06,657 --> 00:42:10,494
it made me think I still had you.

760
00:42:12,763 --> 00:42:14,431
It encouraged me to keep going.

761
00:42:16,700 --> 00:42:18,035
I, um…

762
00:42:22,673 --> 00:42:23,841
Thank you.

763
00:42:24,675 --> 00:42:25,709
Well…

764
00:42:34,018 --> 00:42:36,820
Where's Masato today?

765
00:42:38,622 --> 00:42:41,425
My father is looking after him,
so it's okay.

766
00:42:50,301 --> 00:42:51,902
Rumpy-pumpy is on, isn't it?

767
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:59,910
<i>I'm in a pickle. What should I do?</i>

768
00:42:59,977 --> 00:43:02,212
<i>Am I already going to meet her father?</i>

769
00:43:02,780 --> 00:43:05,382
<i>Anyway, I should refrain
from drinking any more.</i>

770
00:43:05,950 --> 00:43:07,451
<i>Wait, am I going to do the deed?</i>

771
00:43:07,518 --> 00:43:10,454
<i>Since when? Since what? Is it okay?</i>

772
00:43:11,322 --> 00:43:15,392
Why not? Even I want to enjoy
some romance sometimes.

773
00:43:15,459 --> 00:43:16,327
MOM

774
00:43:18,495 --> 00:43:20,831
<i>What am I calling her for?
What will I say?</i>

775
00:43:20,898 --> 00:43:24,902
<i>Am I going to ask Junko
if I can have rumpy-pumpy?</i>

776
00:43:25,603 --> 00:43:26,804
No signal?

777
00:43:56,700 --> 00:43:58,435
Huh? Where's Mr. Ogawa?

778
00:43:59,670 --> 00:44:01,572
He said he was going
to get some fresh air.

779
00:44:03,307 --> 00:44:04,141
Ow!

780
00:44:21,258 --> 00:44:23,260
"NANTETTATTE IDOL"
KYOKO KOIZUMI

781
00:44:24,428 --> 00:44:25,896
No way.

782
00:44:28,298 --> 00:44:31,301
Are you okay? Are you drunk, Mr. Ogawa?

783
00:44:32,336 --> 00:44:34,471
Huh? What?

784
00:44:40,344 --> 00:44:41,345
What year is it?

785
00:44:41,979 --> 00:44:43,013
Showa 61.

786
00:44:43,080 --> 00:44:44,448
Subtitle translation by: Ai Matsuoka

787
00:44:44,515 --> 00:44:45,716
What?!

788
00:44:45,783 --> 00:44:47,084
Time to make my rounds!

789
00:44:47,151 --> 00:44:48,686
It's the most extreme show right now.

790
00:44:48,752 --> 00:44:50,587
-What are you doing here?
-Huh?

791
00:44:50,654 --> 00:44:52,589
Please don't.
It will get taken out of context.

792
00:44:53,090 --> 00:44:55,092
An inappropriate remark was made.

793
00:44:55,159 --> 00:44:56,260
Cut the crap already!

794
00:44:56,326 --> 00:44:57,194
Right back at you!

795
00:44:57,261 --> 00:44:59,129
You've fallen in love, haven't you?

796
00:44:59,196 --> 00:45:00,731
I promise I'll return.

